{"type": "article", "id": 18026, "title": "金属隔断", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-25T06:50:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060026103qOjIS9C1TV7WZYe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一套金属做的动物隔断，来自意大利的设计品牌 da a。采用激光切割金属板材制作，用有规则的几何镂空勾勒出猫头鹰和兔子两种样式，像是立体的剪纸，很有艺术感。其中，猫头鹰有 1.8m 高，是完全对称的，而兔子的两只耳朵打破了这种对称，有 2.25m 高，更适合放在户外。<a href=\"http://www.daaitalia.com/en/product/anacleto/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002607goucz9Zf157AF20G.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002608WR9CMLxk1h65TyrK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33496333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002609syFNBGk6RZTr8XuH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.86797066\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002609pEnJN75s1rxuaFti.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.33481646\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}